  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    This strategy focuses on modernizing and streamlining the application environment&amp;nbsp;in order to reduce costs and&#xD;
    remain competitive, with minimal disruption to the business.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Symptoms that indicate the need to&amp;nbsp;modernize applications&amp;nbsp;include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Applications that no longer serve key business needs.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Key business functionality that is embedded in brittle, inflexible applications that are not easily reused or extended (which is difficult and expensive to maintain).&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Patchwork of systems and platforms, each with unique maintenance needs.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solutions&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following solutions help to modernize applications:&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    High Impact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_ui_modernization_88264BD3.html&quot; guid=&quot;_qcHTILbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application UI Modernization&lt;/a> - Extend the value of existing solutions in a cost&#xD;
        effective manner by modernizing their user interfaces&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_transformation_6C08D1F9.html&quot; guid=&quot;_uyUeYLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Transformation&lt;/a> - Transform applications using modern architectures&#xD;
        and technologies while leveraging existing investments.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/rearchitect_for_reuse_503CC74C.html&quot; guid=&quot;_Gc7bsMyEEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Re-Architect for Reuse&lt;/a> - Re-architect existing solutions to improve reusability&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_re-platforming_FDA9E88B.html&quot; guid=&quot;_yVtsoLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Re-Platforming&lt;/a> - Move applications to more modern platforms&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/optimizing_server_utilization_5D37BA9E.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xDOpYOaREd6w5Z3dNqpXmw&quot;>Optimizing Server Utilization&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Optimize server workloads to maximize the&#xD;
        value returned by the server infrastructure to the business.&lt;br />&#xD;
        &lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
